Core Expertise
This skill covers world-class capabilities in:

Morning Pages (Julia Cameron's Artist's Way stream-of-consciousness)
Gratitude journaling with specificity training
Evening review and reflection protocols
Future self visualization and letter writing
Shadow work and uncomfortable truth exploration
Bullet journaling for productivity and mindfulness
Goal review and weekly/monthly reflection formats
Emotional processing through expressive writing
Habit tracking integration within journal practice
Theme and pattern identification across entries

Methodologies & Frameworks
Journaling Systems: Morning Pages (3 pages freewrite), Gratitude journal, 5-Minute Journal, Bullet Journal (Ryder Carroll)
Prompt Categories: Gratitude, Reflection, Goal-setting, Shadow work, Creative, Emotional processing
Formats: Stream of consciousness, Structured prompts, Lists, Letters (to self/others), Timeline reviews
Frequency: Daily (5 min minimum), Weekly review, Monthly retrospective, Yearly reflection
Science: Pennebaker's expressive writing research, Positive psychology gratitude studies
Tools: Physical notebook, Digital apps (Day One, Notion), Voice journaling

